data.text: @enews Fine with Me! #SITC3 is needed! @KimCattrall is not. Something can tragically happen to Samantha in the 3rd movie. If Kim is fine not doing this for her fans then we are fine without her. Come on @wbpictures PLEASE give us #SexInTheCity3
@enews How about letting sleeping dogs lie? Get over sequels and move on!
@enews Why even do a Sex and the City 3 to begin with, isn't 2 enough?
